建立回归模型¶

In [5]:
X=bank_data['各项贷款余额'].values.reshape(-1,1)
y=bank_data['不良贷款（亿元）'].values.reshape(-1,1)
In [6]:
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression

sl_model=LinearRegression()
sl_model.fit(X,y)
Out[6]:
LinearRegression()

二元线性回归的示意图¶

In [18]:
x = bank_data['各项贷款余额']
y = bank_data['本年累计应收贷款（亿元）']
z = bank_data['不良贷款（亿元）']

In [26]:
#三维散点图
%matplotlib notebook
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt
from mpl_toolkits.mplot3d import Axes3D

# 创建一个三维的绘图工程
ax = plt.subplot(111, projection='3d')
ax.scatter(x, y, z)

ax.set_xlabel('x1:各项贷款余额')
ax.set_ylabel('x2:本年累计应收贷款')
ax.set_zlabel('y:不良贷款')

plt.show()
In [21]:
from sklearn.linear_model import LinearRegression

X=bank_data.iloc[:,1:3]
y=bank_data.iloc[:,0]

ml_model=LinearRegression()
ml_model.fit(X,y)

coef=ml_model.coef_
intercept=ml_model.intercept_
print(coef)
print(intercept)

[0.02890939 0.1678986 ]
-1.3788341356629874
In [27]:
%matplotlib notebook
import numpy as np

ax = plt.subplot(111, projection='3d')
# 绘制数据点
ax.scatter(x, y, z)

#绘制拟合平面
xx=np.linspace(0, 350, 1000)
yy=np.linspace(0, 12, 100)
xx,yy=np.meshgrid(xx,yy)
#回归方程：拟合平面
zz=coef[0]*xx+coef[1]*yy+intercept
ax.plot_surface(xx, yy, zz,alpha=0.3)

ax.set_xlabel('x1:各项贷款余额')
ax.set_ylabel('x2:本年累计应收贷款')
ax.set_zlabel('y:不良贷款')

plt.show()
